name: Alex Johnson
summary: Alex Johnson, a 34-year-old non-binary individual, works as a Software Developer in the technology industry. They graduated from Columbia University and currently reside in Los Angeles, California but hail from Chicago, Illinois. Alex, who is of Black African Descent, is an ENFP Gemini who is fluent in English and Spanish. They are agnostic, lean towards liberal politics, and highly value family, equality, and personal growth. Their interests include traveling, coding, video games, and cooking. While they do not currently have children, they do want them in the future. Alex is a pet parent to a dog and their lifestyle habits include being active, drinking occasionally, smoking marijuana, but refraining from cigarettes and other drugs. In terms of a partner, they're looking for someone else who is between 30-40, doesn't smoke, is open to having children, and enjoys exercising from time to time.
